```
Implement database connection pool settings via environment variables:
- `DB_POOL_SIZE`: 10 (default)
- `DB_MAX_OVERFLOW`: 20 (default)
- `DB_POOL_TIMEOUT`: 30 seconds (default)
- `DB_POOL_RECYCLE`: 1800 seconds (default)

Introduce a task semaphore to limit concurrent background operations that might use DB connections.
```
